OL,6,FA mother from Brighton says she's
OL,7,Fextremely concerned about her son's
OL,8,Fhealth because of severe mould, leaks
OL,9,Fand condensation in her flat.
OL,11,FSinead Pope's son has asthma and other
OL,12,Fmedical problems.
OL,14,FShe has told ITV Meridian the issues
OL,15,Fhave been going on ever since she
OL,16,Fmoved in four years ago.
